.TH "snd_hda_spdif_ctls_assign" 9 "snd_hda_spdif_ctls_assign" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hda_spdif_ctls_assign \- Assign the SPDIF controls to the given NID
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" snd_hda_spdif_ctls_assign
.BI "(struct hda_codec *codec "  ","
.BI "int idx "  ","
.BI "hda_nid_t nid "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "codec" 12
the HDA codec
.IP "idx" 12
the SPDIF ctl idx
.IP "nid" 12
widget NID
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Assign the widget to the SPDIF control with the given index.
